	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I can hear a 20KHz sine wave, and can kind of feel a 23KHz sine wave. ;b
<br />
<br />A super-sonic sound may be considered inaudible if it's playing by itself, but interference with other channels can produce additional, barely audible tones.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


